Step 1: Create Graded Page pt. 2

- Select Submits per day. Change the indicator to Avg Days to Grade, goal will be Avg Days to Grade goal. Color coding should be low is good.

- Copy and paste background in sub vs graded kpi, change out the values to avg days to grade




- Select the top visual and change the column values to Sub vs Graded and Sub vs Non Graded (make sure to remove the periods at the beginning.

- Change title to Sub vs Graded, Sub vs Non Graded
